IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. PERFDEMO.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    PERFORM INIT-PARA.
    PERFORM INIT-PARA THROUGH CLEANUP-PARA.
    PERFORM WORK-PARA 5 TIMES.
    PERFORM UNTIL WS-DONE = 1
        ADD 1 TO WS-A
    END-PERFORM.
    PERFORM WITH TEST AFTER UNTIL WS-A > 10
        ADD 1 TO WS-A
    END-PERFORM.
    PERFORM VARYING WS-I FROM 1 BY 1 UNTIL WS-I > 10
        DISPLAY WS-I
    END-PERFORM.
    PERFORM 3 TIMES
        DISPLAY "x"
    END-PERFORM.
    PERFORM
        MOVE 0 TO WS-A
        DISPLAY WS-A
    END-PERFORM.
    STOP RUN.
